  "remarks": "TAi.049 Title: Maulavi. Designation: a) Deputy (Cultural) Minister of Information and Culture of the Taliban regime, b) Head of Consular Department of Ministry of Foreign Affairs under the Taliban regime. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Hottak tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 29 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended on 9 July 2007, 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011)",
